  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 268bf36e2c95048f4b4ca0fcdf827688, type: 3}
  m_Name: Resident 3A
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::DialogueData
  SpeakerName: Dialogue
  lines:
  - Hey I also been having issues with an outlet in my kitchen by my microwave. I
    only use my microwave on that outlet.
  - It was fine a couple days ago but then it just stopped working when I plugged
    in a Blender in the same socket.
  - It seems like the outlet is short circuited and I have no Idea why can you check
    it out? (Check circuit breaker for kitchen)
